data_findings.finding: Best submission score ~0.78 achieved with hard voting ensemble. Key features: Title extracted from Name, FamilySize (SibSp+Parch+1), IsAlone binary, Age/Fare binning. Models: Decision Tree, Random Forest, AdaBoost, GradientBoosting, XGBoost all converge around same accuracy after tuning.
